--HOW TO RUN--
1. Run command: cargo build
2. run executable at target/debug/media_player.exe
    media_player.exe <path to your music folder>
3. App will prompt you to enter your music folder again. This does not work!! But you may input whatever you
    like and it will display a nice message :)
4. To access the menu bar press ESCAPE
5. Music files will be sorted in hierarchical arder (ARTIST -> ALBUM -> SONG)
5. Selecting either an artist or album from the menu bar will display its contents in a table